Imprisoner/Predator/Choran:



Imprisoner looked to Spitfire.  "That, is none of your concern.  Where we are 
going, is none of anyone of your concerns." he said, looking to the three 
Maximals in front of him.

Predator chimed in.  "If you keep stalking us, we will execute you like 
cyber-ducks in a barrel."

"You have been warned." Choran said in his gurgly voice.

The Predacons continued heading for the Ark.
